All Implemented Interfaces:
DisplayChangeListenable, PropertyChangeListenable, Serializable, Cloneable
public class LabeledStructureEdge
extends DefaultListenableEdge

This class defines a LabeledGraphEdge, which is a GrALoG-Edge, that has a label. It can be seen as an example of how to implement edgeTypes in GrALoG.
